summary: This document is a customer experience survey notification from Fifth Third Bank, thanking customers for choosing them as a mortgage loan provider and inviting them to participate in a survey conducted by ath Power Consulting. It emphasizes the bank's commitment to customer service and assures customers that their personal information will remain confidential.
keyFacts: The document is a notification for a customer experience survey.
Fifth Third Bank is the mortgage loan provider mentioned.
ath Power Consulting is the company conducting the survey.
The survey aims to gather feedback to improve product and service levels.
Fifth Third Bank assures customers that their personal information will not be shared.
